### **Capital Raising Announcement Summary**  

- **Type:** Placement  
- **Amount Raised:** AUD $3.7 million (before costs)  
- **Issue Price:** $0.031 per share  
- **Shares Issued:** 120.0 million new shares  
- **Discount/Premium:**  
  - **11.4% discount** to last close ($0.035 on 7 July 2025)  
  - **0.7% premium** to 15-day VWAP ($0.0308)  
- **Use of Proceeds:**  
  - Advancing **Judith-2 Well** to Final Investment Decision  
  - Securing **Valaris 107** jack-up rig option fee  
  - Long-lead items (wellhead) & working capital  
- **Timetable:**  
  - **Settlement:** 15 July 2025  
  - **Allotment & Quotation:** ~16 July 2025  
- **Key Catalyst:** Independent GaffneyCline certification of **166 BCF 2C Contingent Resource** & **1.86 TCF P50 Prospective Resource** in Judith Gas Field (Gippsland Basin)  
- **Strategic Next Steps:**  
  - **Appraisal well (Judith-2)** targeting mid-2026 drilling  
  - **Farm-out process** to attract development partners
